high_descs: Go across the room to the kitchen then go to the sink on the right side.
Pick up the egg that is beside the fork in the sink.
Move across the kitchen to the refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator, then place the egg on the glass shelf and close the fridge. Wait then open the fridge and pick up the egg, then close the fridge.
Move across the kitchen to the sink.
Put the egg in the sink beside the fork.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled egg into the sink.

high_descs: Go straight across the room, and then right to go around the island and find the sink on the right.
Pick up the egg in the back of the sink.
Take the egg and turn right to find the fridge on the right.
Place the egg inside the fridge. Then open the door and take out the egg. Shut the fridge door.
Take the egg and turn right, then right again at the sink.
Place the egg back into the sink.
anns.task_desc: Chill an egg and place it in the sink.
